ts/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e377bd919bc87090ebf596456dea204c12353c9b","tid":207580,"uid":4326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T04:36:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>喺外地遇到自己人唔係通常都好開心好熱情嘅咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n證明你沒去過旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n試過去台灣旅行比香港人叫我幫佢影相<br />\n起初佢以為我係台灣人, 勁好態度<br />\n之後我同佢講廣東話, 即刻180度轉變<br />\n好似老奉幫佢影咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n個人係3X-4X歲女性</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你係港男，就應份服待港女啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n下次再有呢D情況, 我會幫呢D人影到OUT FOCUS<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n比返部相機/手機佢 之後即走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n記有得位巴打幫強國人影相<br />\n<br />\n又叫佢小心啲話識唔識影個啲<br />\n<br />\n跟住個巴打慢慢影其實係幫佢del 鳩曬啲相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed59a1396961a68185e82d3dbc79db37c1806f0d","tid":207580,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T04:40:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>會唔會係以為佢係大陸人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n部分台灣人唔係=大陸人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有好幾個可能性<br />\n店員係台灣人,以為佢係大陸人<br />\n店