like":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T05:27:27.000Z","msg":"不嬲中國人最睇唔起就係中國人<br />\n欺壓剝削中國人最犀利就係中國人自己<br />\n不論自己地方或者外國都係咁"},{"pid":"4efd49de980e50aec0b62123a6ea498162328d68","tid":207580,"uid":18753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T05:46:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>喺外地遇到自己人唔係通常都好開心好熱情嘅咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n證明你沒去過旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但係我旅行遇到自己人我會幾開心喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係瑞士遇到日本人叫我幫佢影好有禮貌，仲主動話幫我影先<br />\n遇到香港人我幫完佢就一句唔該走急急腳左去，先叫佢幫我影翻都叫唔切<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b47a0fb8c6e49f0023a9c2f75cae4edd9875f0e","tid":207580,"uid":23284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T05:47:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>喺外地遇到自己人唔係通常都好開心好熱情嘅咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n證明你沒去過旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nExchange果時有間成日去既鋪頭係香港人開都會吹下水，去歐遊都撞過有香港後生仔打工傾得好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過最憎見到中國土豪係真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c10da3ec019b0eea22acd02855673a7dcd62248","tid":207580,"uid":99805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T05:55:23.000Z","msg":"我去日本聽到廣東話我想嘔<br />\n<br />\n利申:我啞的"},{"pid":"e8edcd0208570764558f73532fc57df8b9c29093","tid":207580,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T05:57:57.000Z","msg":"tvbs<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e79969e0c0840950125e5290049962ddc55855ab","tid":207580,"uid":13257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T05:59:28.000Z","msg":"樓上忍痛兩個字都有得嘈"},{"pid":"9175fa184