ckquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>喺外地遇到自己人唔係通常都好開心好熱情嘅咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n證明你沒去過旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇咩人、咩情況啦，有時大家互相幫忙係好事嚟</blockquote><br />\n我試過喺歐洲遇到個移民潮嗰陣過左去嘅伯伯 傾左15分鐘計 佢係咁問我香港依家點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢話佢嗰邊都越黎越唔好住 啲野俾大陸人炒貴曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有大陸人既地方都唔會好住 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a29ceab575404f1eec4649a90d85bc5abe2b89b1","tid":207580,"uid":2613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T06:17:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去到歐洲都要買珍珠奶茶飲，自己係台灣未飲夠咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你係外國住得耐<br />\n你就會明白突然想食一碗叉燒飯感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daa68d6f8948381fb225e0770f876b009de49bf9","tid":207580,"uid":2076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T06:17:30.000Z","msg":"台狗不嬲都媚外"},{"pid":"71cdcd6720fcf6503ed2d877ded480214e901acf","tid":207580,"uid":55951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T06:24:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>台狗不嬲都媚外</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/gK8EW_g_4HI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FgK8EW_g_4HI&d=%2FOWxXeQsMLcQIgbDBmmt7ttKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=e60f2a14\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/gK8EW_g_4HI</a>"},{"pid":"92fd69ba029038bb1bbc580b718b7079fc938193","tid":207580,"uid":683,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T06:25:47.000Z","msg":"台灣最美麗的風景是人，串鳩台灣人=串鳩台灣風景=串鳩台灣旅遊業=串鳩民主大國=樓主係五毛<br />\n<br />\n你條無民主既五毛死港豬有咩資格對民主大國指手劃腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 返去奶共啦你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hk