gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果一杯珍珠奶茶賣到&pound;10嘅話，我都走去賣奶茶算喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌那媽，人地辻利喺SOHO一杯抹茶新地都係賣到&pound;5左右之嘛<br />\n10鎊一杯珍珠奶茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"661a9aa8ad16458f425269d6b1c32c746f02ada4","tid":207580,"uid":38540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T07:52:08.000Z","msg":"其實香港都係啦 鬼佬客特別好笑容 只怪你不是洋腸"},{"pid":"68e0d6ef038a1dbdc0070c2a9d0c0d08e7d1177f","tid":207580,"uid":103229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T07:55:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>要忍痛買150台幣珍珠奶茶...都知條人妻咩質素.....</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你知唔知台灣買杯珍珠奶茶要幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢而家係台灣買咩？ 住左咁耐西班牙 唔係唔知果邊物價啊？ 倫敦都要10鎊 佢咪要跳樓？</blockquote><br />\n&pound;10？巴打你住邊呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> London chatime regular size 比盡&pound;3.5喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果一杯珍珠奶茶賣到&pound;10嘅話，我都走去賣奶茶算喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌那媽，人地辻利喺SOHO一杯抹茶新地都係賣到&pound;5左右之嘛<br />\n10鎊一杯珍珠奶茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n食個叉雞飯都係&pound;7-8 飲杯奶茶要&pound;10<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 下次做好功課再衝出黎叻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"079db749baddcc63e21389f8181d9cafa34cceb5","tid":207580,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T07:55:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>喺外地遇到自己人唔係通常都好開心好熱情嘅咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n證明你沒去過旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但係我旅行遇到自己人我會幾開心喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係瑞士遇到日本人叫我幫佢影好有禮貌，仲主動話幫我影先<br />\n遇到香港人我幫完佢就一句唔該走急急腳左去，先叫佢幫我影翻都叫唔切<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我覺得講左唔該已經好好喇喎 你自己叫唔切又入人數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5145b5e0c8a22fc38db8eb5c22b5b1af32e2ce34","tid":207580,"uid":55990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T07:56:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c45970d87d8058cf16a12a1199ebd6a1cca7a4d4","tid":207580,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T07:56:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試過去日本買野 個收銀態度勁差問佢係咪免税又就咁指個牌 成程西口西面一句野都冇講過 找錢就咁扔係個盤 <br />\n本身以為佢心情唔好 點知對住下一個本地客即刻轉哂態度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁你要多謝d 支那人"},{"pid":"b3370395b3526e956de4ba9e629b9c6e12f2ac9f","tid":207580,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T07:57:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前一條友去神戶旅行，山上面嘅巴士站撞到對香港中年夫妻等緊車，我聽佢地用廣東話先埋去禮貌咁問邊到有車上山，點撚知一句  下唔知喎  就完，我屌佢地老母</blockquote><br />\n咁人地唔知 仲可以答你d 咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d184f9129e42bba787a3f3147c334b43ff56c820","tid":207580,"uid":31389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T08:07:13.000Z","msg":"難怪亞洲人比人睇唔起<br />\n自己人都睇唔起自己人點會得人尊重"},{"pid":"6b8a162d9d49c95be757c938044e750cf5b09f30","tid":207580,"uid":8203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T08:08:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>喺外地遇到自己人唔係通常都好開心好熱情嘅咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n證明你沒去過旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n試過去台灣旅行比香港人叫我幫佢影相<br />\n起初佢以為我係台灣人, 勁好態度<br />\n之後我同佢講廣東話, 即刻180度轉變<br />\n好似老奉幫佢影咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n個人係3X-4X歲女性</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你係港男，就應份服待港女啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n下次再有呢D情況, 我會幫呢D人影到OUT FOCUS<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n比返部相機/手機佢 之後即走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我會咩都唔講咁攤開隻手<br />\n等佢放低部機我就即刻縮手<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68617993bda6d0bd20265652b1cd6ab4d8b34a40","tid":207580,"uid":8203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T08:11:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試過去日本買野 個收銀態度勁差問佢係咪免税又就咁指個牌 成程西口西面一句野都冇講過 找錢就咁扔係個盤 <br />\n本身以為佢心情唔好 點知對住下一個本地客即刻轉哂態度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n得罪講句 <br />\n有機會好多香港人出國丟架搞到咁"},{"pid":"24807e1af5382fbd78f273cc0e4821f02ab0a4d0","tid":207580,"uid":11148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T08:23:00.000Z","msg":"支那人連累成個亞洲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0764b0631134170824bd8a43b4f2d6dcc3a65cea","tid":207580,"uid":63001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T08:24:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>試過去日本買野 個收銀態度勁差問佢係咪免税又就咁指個牌 成程西口西面一句野都冇講過 找錢就咁扔係個盤 <br />\n本身以為佢心情唔好 點知對住下一個本地客即刻轉哂態度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大阪？</blockquote><br />\n我反而試過係大阪藥妝店收銀係香港人，見我係香港人本身閪口閪面變笑笑口仲同我吹水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可能真係我好彩啦"},{"pid":"e58482b1770a9405bd63738a8122b1d7f5fb666e","tid":207580,"uid":41693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T08:51:10.000Z","msg":"睇人"},{"pid":"2749da257246b2568b3239ad08520ecacd1494e2","tid":207580,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T09:43:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0ef629f405478dd6307cbf75920d1fd78e632e9f","tid":207580,"uid":988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T04:08:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>要忍痛買150台幣珍珠奶茶...都知條人妻咩質素.....</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你知唔知台灣買杯珍珠奶茶要幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢而家係台灣買咩？ 住左咁耐西班牙 唔係唔知果邊物價啊？ 倫敦都要10鎊 佢咪要跳樓？</blockquote><br />\n&pound;10？巴打你住邊呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> London chatime regular size 比盡&pound;3.5喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我之前係Bubbleology 飲一杯大珍珠奶茶 真係要我10.5磅wo...不過我另外加左仙草 朱古力條果d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83e4c884615b046f54816aecf1cfff8cc2648143","tid":207580,"uid":26671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T05:04:04.000Z","msg":"試過係荷蘭小城食野遇到過左去幾十年嘅香港人店主，幾好人仲請我飲野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef144cf659fb0650054b85129307bdf0780f686e","tid":207580,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T06:30:52.000Z","msg":"其實我明個店員心態<br />\n應該係因為你一黎就同人講中文<br />\n人地先覺得你黎到外國都唔用人地國家語言先卑視你<br />\n如果佢一開始用返果個國家既語言叫野飲 然後先問人地係咪台灣人先再講返中文 應該唔會咁既反應"},{"pid":"17dd753572bb6251e804d8e73122ba6f21541570","tid":207580,"uid":12013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T06:35:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>去到歐洲都要買珍珠奶茶飲，自己係台灣未飲夠咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你係外國住得耐<br />\n你就會明白突然想食一碗叉燒飯感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我好明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}